attr.title: Psebay
attr.desc: Psebay is an atmospheric adventure in moto trial genre. Features exciting gameplay with dynamic gravity, special atmosphere and unique sound, stunning scenery in silhouette style, and comfortable and easy controls.
attr.inst: Purchase and download the game from Steam and copy all game files into the assets folder. You can also use the free demo
attr.inst_md: Purchase and download the game from [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/608660/Psebay/) and copy all game files into the `assets` folder. You can also use the free demo
